{"page":1,"results":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":2905749,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Benjamin Mousquet","original_name":"Benjamin Mousquet","popularity":0.094,"profile_path":"/khzkKmVFv3VimQzUTbAxPLmyNqq.jpg","known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/7neeXze9HB3MTxDYyh3wwysydMN.jpg","id":778855,"title":"Chickenhare and the Hamster of Darkness","original_title":"Chickenhare and the Hamster of Darkness","overview":"Young Chickenhare is the adopted son of King Peter, a famous adventurer. Part chicken and part hare, he has a really tough time growing up and disguises himself as a hare to avoid the mockeries of his peers. When the day of the Royal Adventurer Society trials comes, Chickenhare, hampered by his disguise, fails miserably. But he is determined to grab a second chance and find the Scepter of the Hamster of Darkness, before his evil Uncle Lapin. The Scepter will give immense power to its holder. If Lapin gets hold of it, he will be unstoppable. Accompanied by his faithful servant Abe, a sarcastic turtle, and Meg, a martial arts expert skunk, he sets of on an epic and initiatory quest.","poster_path":"/2v6f1EqTo4FUxVT9MDXpF6158AX.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"en","genre_ids":[16,12,35,10751,14],"popularity":2.7679,"release_date":"2022-02-16","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":7.258,"vote_count":285},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/fnuJV4WwxGM8w784lGV7j32JVsG.jpg","id":1215532,"title":"Chickenhare and the Secret of the Groundhog","original_title":"Chickenhare and the Secret of the Groundhog","overview":"Chickenhare embarks on an epic quest, a mysterious groundhog with the power to reverse time and save his species. His adventure takes a dangerous turn when his group discover they are not the only ones searching for this ancient power.","poster_path":"/cUCwWxHF1bRfqeY7beZfsvT7WBR.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"en","genre_ids":[16,12,35,10751],"popularity":5.9505,"release_date":"2025-09-19","softcor